  <Summary>The ghost of Alan Granger kills his girlfriend and resume's Alan's life, but the ghost of his girlfriend Sheila has her revenge.

A famed physicist and his assistant have discovered that life exists deep within the Earth and have made contact with it. To prove their findings, they must excavate and see if they can find the "being" they've made contact with.

A strange man sells tiny people to three puppeteers to use in their act.

Simon creates lifelike wax figures by pouring was over live people.  The wax figures return to life to enact their revenge.

Various superstitions are looked at.</Summary>
